28
00:01:49.067 --> 00:01:50.317
- You fucking…
- Hey! Stop

29
00:01:50.318 --> 00:01:51.568
You little shit!

30
00:01:51.569 --> 00:01:53.028
I'm gonna fuckin' murder you.

31
