204
00:10:18.701 --> 00:10:19.660
Is it still working?

205
00:10:21.495 --> 00:10:22.537
Yeah.

206
00:10:24.248 --> 00:10:25.124
Yeah.

207
00:10:29.795 --> 00:10:31.589
Aruna. my diva.

208
00:10:32.423 --> 00:10:34.841
How are you. mama?

209
00:10:34.842 --> 00:10:36.801
You didn't go with the team to Boston?

210
00:10:36.802 --> 00:10:38.346
And be away from my bestie?

211
00:10:40.181 --> 00:10:42.390
