219
00:11:07.875 --> 00:11:09.877
I see what you're trying to do here.

220
00:11:10.836 --> 00:11:12.713
- And I will keep your secret.
- Oh my God.

221
00:11:13.631 --> 00:11:14.923
Thank you. Aruna.

222
00:11:14.924 --> 00:11:17.133
Unless someone asks me. Then I cannot lie.

223
00:11:17.134 --> 00:11:18.385
What?

224
00:11:18.386 --> 00:11:19.969
No. Why?

225
00:11:19.970 --> 00:11:21.597
I don't have your family's loose morals.

226
00:11:22.181 --> 00:11:24.057
No. neither do I. I'm the good one.

227
00:11:24.058 --> 00:11:26.018
Whatever you have to tell yourself.

228
00:11:32.191 --> 00:11:33.316
Oh God.

229
00:11:33.317 --> 00:11:36.778
{\an8}<i>And LA loses game three
of the finals in Boston.</i>

230
00:11:36.779 --> 00:11:38.738
