232
00:11:39.824 --> 00:11:41.116
No. it is not over.

233
00:11:41.117 --> 00:11:44.661
Yes. we are down three games to none.
Yes. no one's ever come back from that.

234
00:11:44.662 --> 00:11:47.665
But your blowout's still holding up.

235
00:11:51.460 --> 00:11:53.420
- What the…?
- Jay?!

236
00:11:53.421 --> 00:11:55.255
Oh. hey. this is nuts.

237
00:11:55.256 --> 00:11:57.549
I. uh. thought this was my room.

238
00:11:57.550 --> 00:11:59.884
